# Preserve committed line endings.
#
# The repository already contains a mix of CRLF and LF files. For this private
# project, Git should not treat historical EOL differences as dirty worktree
# changes. Keep EOL bytes as-is instead of running text normalization filters.
* -text

# Binary files should not be normalized.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.mp3 binary
*.mp4 binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.ico binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
